        <h2>What is our project?</h2>
          <p class = "answer"><span>Our final project is a website and game dedicated to educating viewers and players on political views,
          <br>as well as aligning their views with a 2020 Presidential Candidate.<br>
          <br>We hope to have created an unbiased, informative source of education and information.
          <br>The website provides information on the project, download for the game, and information on the Presidential Candidates.
          <br><br>The game is setup as a visual novel, but is geared more towards introducing differing sides on issues rather than creating a narrative.</span></p>
        <h2>How did we make our project?</h2>
          <p class = "answer">We used HTML, CSS, and Javascript to create the website.
          <br>For the game, we used the program RenPy, which uses a language based on Python.</p>
